// established convention here, but simplified to a single flat schema --
// D1 has no multi-schema/RLS/RPC concept, so the old
// graphql_public/__InternalSupabase/Functions/Enums scaffolding is gone.
// Update this file by hand alongside each new migration in goodLuckAdmin's
// migrations/*.sql (that repo owns the schema; this is just the D1 type
// mirror consumed here).
